from rjg richard griffith subject re burden of proof in ray bill ray write if i make a statement that god exist love me etc but in no way insist that you believe it do that place a burden of proof upon me if you insist that god do exist do that place a burden of proof upon you i give no proof i only give testimony to my belief i will respond to proof that you attempt to disprove my belief what be ymy reaction to person who claim they be abduct by space alien some of these person say i wa abduct experiment on etc if we insist that these alien do exist be the burden of proof place on u these person can give no hard fact but can give a lot of testimony to back up their belief replace space alien with elvi big foot blue unicorn and we have a larger percentage of the population than i like to think about sometime i wonder if reality really be a different experience for everone 